description._content: Item Description: Employees and officers of Ladd and Bush Bank of Salem, Oregon, are shown helping the community bean picking campaign following the bank closure. Original Collection: Harriet's Collection Item Number: HC 972 You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more? You can find more digital resources online.
